# Remoroo blocklist — paths here are hidden from the agent.
# Same syntax as .gitignore. Edit by hand or via `remoroo block <pattern>`.
# To disable Remoroo's privacy guard entirely, leave this file empty.

# Recommended defaults (auto-seeded on first run):
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
id_rsa*
*.crt
secrets/
.aws/
.ssh/
credentials*
.netrc
.npmrc
*.kdbx
